Package it.unipr.sowide.java.structures

package it.unipr.sowide.java.structures
Provides some classes used for describing the Java language expressions and structures.
  • Classes

    Description
    ArithmeticDemo
    The ArithmeticDemo class defines a demo of the use of the arithmetic operators.
    ArrayDemo
    The ArrayDemo class defines a demo of the use of arrays.

    The ConditionalDemo class defines a demo of the use of the conditional statements and of the relational operators.

    The FactorialDemo class defines a demo of the use of a switch statement for computing the factorial value of a positive integer.
